QuestData.Title: Reloading
QuestData.Description:
Daryl's making every shot count, but there's just too many Horde. We're going to need more ammo soon!
I need you to take this note to my uncle Leo at Deadwash, he'll be able to help.
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the note to Leo Shealds.
QuestData.RewardText: Lea Martin? She's a tough one! I'll try to help her, but we gotta save our people first.
